---
title: Hey!
bodyClass: mcg-home-page
---
{% extends 'layouts/base.njk' %}

{% block main %}
<div class="mcg-wrapper mcg-wrapper--shorter">
  <div class="mcg-avatar">
    <div class="mcg-avatar__wrap">
      <img src="https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/6da168321e6ddbbcf0382e02ceb4989b?s=500" alt="">
    </div>
  </div>
  <h1 class="mcg-sr-only">{{ title }}</h1>
  <p class="mcg-section-heading mcg-mb-md">{{ site.tagline }}</p>
  <p>I'm Levi, a designer, front-end developer, and <a href="./artwork">sometimes artist</a> living in the <a href="https://www.visitbloomington.com/">coolest town in Indiana</a>. I'm currently working to improve the <a href="https://rivet.iu.edu/">user experience of software in higher-ed</a>.</p>
  <p>When something good happens in my life, or I read a good book I try to <a href="./posts">write about it here</a>. I don't feel guilty about how infrequently I post ðŸ˜Š</p>
  
  <h2 class="mcg-sub-heading mcg-mt-md">Weird stuff on Instagram</h2>
  <div class="mcg-mt-sm" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr)">
    {% if site.env == "dev" %}
      {% for image in instagramdev.data %}
      <a href="{{ image.link }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <img src="{{ image.images.thumbnail.url }}" alt="">
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    {% else %}
      {% for image in instagram.data %}
      <a href="{{ image.link }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <img src="{{ image.images.thumbnail.url }}" alt="">
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    {% endif %}
  </div>
  
  <h2 class="mcg-sub-heading mcg-mt-md">Latest posts</h2>
  {% include 'components/recent-posts.njk' %}
</div>
{% endblock %}